Pre-Game Insights: Kane Williamson won't be available for the first match.
England, led by Jos Buttler, aims to commence the tournament with a victory.
Tom Latham and his team seek to begin the competition on a winning note without their captain Kane Williamson.
The England squad boasts exceptional players like Jos Buttler, Liam Livingstone, and Ben Stokes, while New Zealand also fields talents such as Trent Boult, Lockie Ferguson, and Tom Latham.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match will take place at the Narendra Modi Stadium in Ahmedabad.
The match is scheduled for 2:00 PM on Thursday, October 5, 2023.
The pitch report indicates a combination of black and red soil pitches, with the black ones offering good bounce and pace initially, becoming more spinner-friendly as the match progresses.
